data.text:
Embark on an open-world racing adventure in 'Burnout Paradise' on the Xbox 360. Explore a sprawling city, compete in thrilling races, and unleash spectacular crashes in a dynamic environment. It's paradise for adrenaline junkies!

Release Date: March 06, 2007

Genre: Racing
